13 It is hereby enacted by the General Assembly of the State of Vermont:
14 Sec. 1. 20 V.S.A. chapter 88 is added to read:
15 CHAPTER 88. PROTECTION OF VETERANS’ BENEFITS
16 § 1751. LEGISLATIVE INTENT
17 It is the intent of the General Assembly to protect veterans, their
18 dependents, and survivors from paying compensation for assistance with filing
19 veteran-related claims to any person who is not accredited by the U.S.
20 Department of Veterans or providing assistance in their capacity as an
